OL,5,GThe director-general of the BBC Tim
OL,6,GDavie has said that whilst it's
OL,7,G"obviously sad" that three
OL,8,Glong-standing news presenters have
OL,9,Gopted to depart the organisation the
OL,10,Gcurrent level of "management
OL,11,Ginefficiency" needs to be addressed.
OL,13,FYesterday, Deadline reported that BBC
OL,14,FNews presenters David Eades, Joanna
OL,15,FGosling and Tim Willcox have opted to
OL,16,Ftake voluntary redundancy.
OL,3,CBBC boss defends TV news channel merger
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
