PN,35902
SC,0002
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F359A1675177241
OL,5,FThe news came as the BBC continues the
OL,6,Fphased implementation of a merger of
OL,7,Fits international and domestic TV news
OL,8,Fchannels. The official start date for
OL,9,Fthe new channel is believed to be some
OL,10,Ftime in April, though the on-air launch
OL,11,Fis expected to be low-key.
OL,13,FIn July, the BBC announced plans to
OL,14,Fmerge the two TV news channels, as part
OL,15,Fof its new digital-first strategy. Over
OL,16,F70 posts are believed to face the axe
OL,17,Fas a result.
OL,3,CBBC boss defends TV news channel merger
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,E]GArticle Published -- 29-Apr-22 2345
PN,35903
SC,0003
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F359A1675177241
OL,5,FDavie told the Public Accounts
OL,6,FCommittee: "There is a degree of
OL,7,Fmanagement inefficiency, in my view,
OL,8,Fand it is not right, and no one in the
OL,9,Fworld is running completely separate
OL,10,Foperations in this way.
OL,12,F"Now linked to that, I think that it is
OL,13,Fobviously sad when people decide to
OL,14,Ftake VR and leave, but you need less
OL,15,Fpresenters and I think that is
OL,16,Fappropriate.
OL,3,CBBC boss defends TV news channel merger
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,E]GArticle Published -- 29-Apr-22 2345
PN,35904
SC,0004
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F359A1675177241
OL,5,F"Sorry to be blunt. I think we are in a
OL,6,Fposition where we are going to make
OL,7,Fchanges. Some people will leave the
OL,8,FBBC, some people will stay. Actually
OL,9,Fso-called churn in the newsroom is very
OL,10,Flow historically.
OL,12,F"You talk about three outstanding
OL,13,Fpresenters who have chosen to move on,
OL,14,Fthat gives opportunities and allows
OL,15,Fpeople to move through the
OL,16,Forganisation."
OL,18,FMr Davie said he not believe the BBC
OL,19,Fneeded "two completely separate
OL,20,Foperations" and that their merger plans
OL,21,Fweren't just about "digital evangelism"
OL,22,Fbut "based on where the audience is".
OL,3,CBBC boss defends TV news channel merger
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,E]GArticle Published -- 29-Apr-22 2345
PN,35905
SC,0005
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F359A1675177241
OL,5,FHe added: "We don't think it is
OL,6,Fefficient. We think it is absolutely
OL,7,Fappropriate to make the changes to
OL,8,Fclose the independent operations and
OL,9,Frun it as a more integrated operation.
OL,10,FThat does not mean the channel is the
OL,11,Fsame. That would be absurd."
OL,3,CBBC boss defends TV news channel merger
